    <item>
      <title>希尔顿 2024 年盈利预测低于分析师预期</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-07/hilton-s-2024-earnings-forecast-falls-short-of-analyst-estimates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[希尔顿全球控股公司 (Hilton Worldwide Holdings Inc.) 公布的 2024 年预测未达到预期，因为自疫情爆发以来旅行需求经历了起起落落，逐渐趋于正常化。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-07/hilton-s-2024-earnings-forecast-falls-short-of-analyst-estimates</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 07 Feb 2024 11:24:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>艾芬豪成为美国支持的非洲铁路线的首个用户</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-07/ivanhoe-signs-up-to-be-us-backed-african-rail-line-s-first-user</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由亿万富翁罗伯特·弗里德兰 (Robert Friedland) 领导的艾芬豪矿业有限公司 (Ivanhoe Mines Ltd.) 与大宗商品贸易商托克集团 (Trafigura Group) 签署协议，通过铁路将铜从刚果民主共和国运输到邻国安哥拉的洛比托港，这是美国与该铁路项目的首个长期协议政府正在支持。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-07/ivanhoe-signs-up-to-be-us-backed-african-rail-line-s-first-user</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 07 Feb 2024 11:15:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>财报后走势表明投资者对欧洲的期望并不高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-07/post-earnings-moves-show-investors-don-t-expect-much-from-europe</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲的财报季即将迎来至少十年来最糟糕的开局之一，大多数公司公布的业绩均低于预期。但那些在悲观和厄运中带来积极惊喜的人正在收获巨大的回报。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-07/post-earnings-moves-show-investors-don-t-expect-much-from-europe</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 07 Feb 2024 11:13:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>无力偿债的 Signa 房地产部门无法支付自己的清盘费用</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-07/insolvent-signa-real-estate-unit-can-t-pay-for-its-own-wind-up</link>
      <description><![CDATA[西格纳零售和房地产集团的崩溃是如此可怕，以至于即使是受雇来清算破产部门的公司也必须排队才能收回资金。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-07/insolvent-signa-real-estate-unit-can-t-pay-for-its-own-wind-up</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 07 Feb 2024 11:13:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>新的爱马仕牛市摩根士丹利看到更多涨幅创纪录的反弹</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-07/new-hermes-bull-morgan-stanley-sees-more-gains-for-record-rally</link>
      <description><![CDATA[经过多年的观望后，摩根士丹利终于加入看涨行列，推动爱马仕国际股价创下历史新高。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-07/new-hermes-bull-morgan-stanley-sees-more-gains-for-record-rally</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 07 Feb 2024 11:09:44 GMT</pubDate>
