    <item>
      <title>贝莱德的李伟：美联储的目标是将通胀保持在目标水平</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-02-07/fed-s-battle-will-be-keeping-inflation-at-target-wei-li-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[贝莱德全球首席投资策略师李伟讨论了美联储利率前景以及央行降低通胀的努力。李克强在接受彭博电视台采访时表示：“通胀控制在目标水平不难，但保持通胀目标很难。” （来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-02-07/fed-s-battle-will-be-keeping-inflation-at-target-wei-li-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 07 Feb 2024 11:05:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>肯尼亚央行行长认为支持先令遭受重创的空间</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-07/kenya-central-bank-chief-sees-scope-to-support-battered-shilling</link>
      <description><![CDATA[肯尼亚央行行长表示，自去年初以来先令兑美元汇率已贬值近四分之一，其贬值幅度过大，为其提供了支撑空间。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-07/kenya-central-bank-chief-sees-scope-to-support-battered-shilling</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 07 Feb 2024 11:01:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>凯雷调整交易撮合者薪酬，计划回购高达 14 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-07/carlyle-revamps-dealmaker-pay-plans-up-to-1-4-billion-buyback</link>
      <description><![CDATA[凯雷集团 (Carlyle Group Inc.) 正在彻底改革其向交易撮合者付款的方式，以便为股东释放更稳定的现金流，并批准了一项回购高达 14 亿美元股票的计划。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-07/carlyle-revamps-dealmaker-pay-plans-up-to-1-4-billion-buyback</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 07 Feb 2024 11:01:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>习近平试图结束溃败，中国更换了最高市场监管机构</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-07/china-replaces-head-of-securities-regulator-in-surprise-move</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国更换了证券监管机构负责人，这一出人意料的举动可能预示着习近平政府将采取更强有力的措施来结束该国价值 8 万亿美元的股市的暴跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-07/china-replaces-head-of-securities-regulator-in-surprise-move</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 07 Feb 2024 09:26:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>由于房地产风险担忧拖累银行，欧洲股市下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-07/european-stocks-steady-as-traders-weigh-earnings-policy-outlook</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于对银行房地产风险敞口的担忧以及央行行长对提前降息可能性的抵制，欧洲股市小幅走低。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-07/european-stocks-steady-as-traders-weigh-earnings-policy-outlook</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 07 Feb 2024 08:15:45 GMT</pubDate>
